### Key Patterns

**1. Runtime Injection Pattern:**
```typescript
// In runtime.ts
type TelegramChannelRuntime = {
  sendMessageTelegram?: typeof import("./send.js").sendMessageTelegram;
  // ... other optional overrides
};

// In channel.ts
